  <title>Suppressing Header and Footer</title>
  <info>
    <keywordset>
      <keyword>header</keyword>
      <keyword>footer</keyword>
    </keywordset>
    <subjectset>
      <subject>
        <subjectterm>headers</subjectterm>
        <subjectterm>footer</subjectterm>
      </subject>
    </subjectset>
  </info>
   <!--How to remove headers
Von:	Mauritz Jeanson <mj@johanneberg.com>-->
  <section role="problem">
    <title>Problem</title>
    <para>You want to remove your header or footer completely.</para>
  </section>
  <section role="solution">
    <title>Solution</title>
    <para>Insert the following code to remove the header:</para>
    <screen>&lt;xsl:template name="header.content"/></screen>
    <para>The following code removes the footers:</para>
    <screen>&lt;xsl:template name="footer.content"/></screen>
  </section>
